Disorder.CH:
挑战开始后，场地外围会产生等离子场。
角色在等离子场中时，每5秒会受到一次落雷打击，遭受雷元素伤害。
等离子场的范围会随着挑战进程推进而向场地中心扩张。
Disorder.EN:
A Plasma Field will be generated at the edge of the challenge area once the challenge begins.
While within the field, characters will be hit by a lightning strike once every 5s and take Electro DMG.
The area covered by the field will gradually expand as the challenge proceeds.

Disorder.CH:
本层每一间的挑战中，都存在「头目」敌人与拥有护卫它的扈从，为它提供强化效果。
每个扈从会使它的所有元素抗性与物理抗性提高10%；每12秒，扈从会为它恢复生命值，每个扈从能恢复5%生命值。
当场地中不存在扈从时，「头目」敌人会失去上述的强化与恢复效果。
Disorder.EN:
There will be a Leader amongst the opponents present in each challenge on this floor. Its Attendants will also be present to provide it with enhancements and protection.
Each Attendant will increase the Leader's Element RES and Physical RES by 10%. The Attendants will restore the Leader's HP every 12s, with each Attendant restoring 5% HP.
When there are no Attendants, the Leader will not have any of the above enhancement and restoration effects.

队伍中所有角色造成的冰元素伤害提高60%。

Cryo DMG dealt by all party members increased by 60%.

Disorder.CH:
挑战中存在「能量潮汐」，会以10秒为周期，转换「元素满潮」与「元素低潮」。
满潮时，角色的攻击命中敌人时，将产生大量元素微粒，恢复10点元素能量。该效果每2.8秒内至多触发一次。
低潮时，队伍中所有角色无法获取元素能量。
Disorder.EN:
Energy Tides are present in this challenge. They will switch between Elemental High Tide and Elemental Low Tide in 10s cycles.
During High Tide, a large amount of Elemental Particles will be generated when a character's attack hits opponents, restoring 10 Elemental Energy. This effect can occur once every 2.8s.
During Low Tide, all characters in the party cannot gain Elemental Energy.

Disorder.CH:
敌人被击败后，队伍中所有角色会承受「侵蚀」效果。
处于侵蚀状态下的角色将会每秒损失部分生命值。当前场上角色可能会因为侵蚀效果损失的生命值而倒下。处于队伍后台的角色生命值低于15%时，不会因为侵蚀而损失生命值。
侵蚀效果持续10秒，可以叠加，每层效果独立计时。
Disorder.EN:
When opponents are defeated, all party members will be affected by the "Corrosion" status.
Characters being Corroded will lose a fraction of their HP every second. Active characters can be brought down by Corrosion. When a non-active character's HP is less than 15%, they will no longer lose HP due to Corrosion.
Corrosion lasts 10s and can stack. The duration of each stack is counted independently.

Disorder.CH:
敌人的攻击命中当前场上角色后，将为队伍中所有角色施加1层「死寂」效果：立刻损失3%最大生命值。
「死寂」效果持续10秒，每1秒最多施加一次。叠加至10层后，将消耗所有「死寂」效果，使角色损失30%最大生命值。
Disorder.EN:
When the active character is hit by an opponent, all team members gain 1 stack of "Withering": Lose 3% HP immediately.
Withering lasts for 10s and can only be applied once every second. When Withering reaches 10 stacks, all stacks of Withering will be consumed, causing the character to lose 30% HP.
